    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "While those who appreciate bagpipes may like the sound of this gray reed and black leather instrument, its real purpose is to sow turmoil against a performer's enemies, spreading discord with each note. While playing the bagpipes, you gain a +1 item bonus to Performance checks and to Intimidation checks made to Demoralize.",
